artists/drake">Drake</a>等。发行后，它还登上了 Billboard 200 榜首，为 Minaj 带来了她的第四张冠军专辑。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nicki-minaj-pink-friday-2-review-tracklist-lyrics-3555287">这张专辑获得了<i>NME</i>的四星评价</a><i>，</i>尼克·莱文称赞这位皇后说唱歌手作为作词者一贯的卓越表现。 “不过，除此之外，《粉红星期五 2》给人的感觉就像是对米娜所能做的一切的巩固和完善——包括放弃其他艺术家不会想到的流行文化参考，”他写道。 “‘粉红星期五’十三年后，妮琪·米娜并没有失去让我们感到惊讶的能力。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-says-she-would-collaborate-with-taylor-swift-in-a-heartbeat-3562690">妮琪·米娜 (Nicki Minaj) 表示她将“一瞬间”与泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 合作的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 在新讣告中回忆肖恩·麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan)：“我是一名粉丝，纯粹而简单，我将永远如此。” https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-shane-macgowan-obituary-3562664?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nick-cave-shane-macgowan-obituaryEli Ordonez Fri, 22 Dec 2023 04:50:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3562664 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼克·凯夫和肖恩·麦高恩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位后朋克巨星为波格斯主唱写下了第二首由衷的敬意</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-shane-macgowan-obituary-3562664">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 在新讣告中缅怀肖恩·麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 的帖子：“我是一名粉丝，纯粹而简单，我将永远如此”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼克·凯夫和肖恩·麦高恩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nick-cave-shane-macgowan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave)</a>为已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pogues">波格斯</a>主唱肖恩·麦高恩 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shane-macgowan">Shane MacGowan)</a>撰写了新的讣告。<b></b></p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/shane-macgowan-obituary-the-pogues-3551303"><b>Shane MacGowan，1957-2023：一位不妥协、混乱的人</b></a></li></ul><p>作为对<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2023/dec/21/obituaries-2023-shane-macgowan-remembered-by-nick-cave" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《观察家报</em>》 <i>2023 年讣告系列的</i></a>贡献，凯夫为他已故的朋友写了一篇新的悼念文章，这是这位后朋克音乐家在麦高恩去世后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-pens-heartfelt-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-and-sinead-oconnor-3552218">第二次</a>撰写有关他的文章。当<i>《NME》</i>邀请他、MacGowan 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-fall">The Fall 乐队的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-e-smith">Mark E. Smith</a>参加“峰会”时，这篇真诚的文章追溯了他们友谊的起源。</p><p>虽然凯夫公开承认麦高恩酗酒，但他也注意到他令人羡慕且毫不费力的创造力。回忆起他担心麦高恩没有写歌的事例，他“爬过地板，开始在垃圾堆里翻找，直到找到一张纸片”，在纸片上他写下了写给“圣路易斯”的话。 John of Gods”，摘自他 1997 年与 The Popes 合作的专辑“The Crock of Gold”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3559000" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3559000" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3559000" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-1997.jpg" alt="肖恩·麦克高恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-1997.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-1997-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-1997-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-1997-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-1997-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-1997-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3559000" class="wp-caption-text">肖恩·麦高恩（Shane MacGowan） 图片来源：Martyn Goodacre/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “对我来说，他的歌曲真的是非常珍贵的东西，是深刻的艺术作品，但他并没有那样对待它们，”凯夫写道。 “当我日复一日地在办公桌前辛勤工作，尽力生产出我能做的东西时，谢恩的话是通过啤酒托盘和威士忌酒杯传递给他的。”</p><p>凯夫还评论了麦高恩的声音，称其为“他混乱而诗意的灵魂的完美载体”。他接着强调了波格斯乐队在法国音乐节上进行试音的一个例子，写道：“他走到麦克风前，双手插在口袋里唱着《一双棕色的眼睛》，美妙而痛苦的声音就传了出来。”他就像天使的密码一样。目睹这样的事情是一种难得的荣幸。”</p><p>在谈到麦高恩与药物滥用的斗争时，凯夫表达了一种左右为难的感觉，一方面钦佩他坚持“永远搞砸”，另一方面又担心他的状况。 “我从未听到他抱怨宿醉或感觉不好，”凯夫继续说道。 “他只是继续做下去。他从不后悔。我尊重他的这一点，但有时这很困难。有时他身体虚弱，几乎无法正常工作，作为朋友，看到这一点令人心碎。” </p><figure id="attachment_3559001" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3559001" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3559001" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-the-pogues.jpg" alt="肖恩·麦克高恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-the-pogues.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-the-pogues-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-the-pogues-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-the-pogues-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-the-pogues-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/shane-macgowan-the-pogues-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3559001" class="wp-caption-text"> Shane MacGowan 图片来源：Frans Schellekens/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>凯夫最后表示，他是“一个纯粹而简单的粉丝”，并且他“永远都是这样”。尽管如此，他也表示，由于他们之间的牢固纽带，他们的友谊随着时间的推移而加强，他写道：“肖恩与其他人不同。无论他处于什么境地，他都有一种善良，并对我们人类处境的诗意本质有着无法估量的深刻感受。他有一种真理，一种最纯粹的灵魂的清澈。你无法隐藏这样的事情。”</p><p>麦高恩于 11 月 30 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-line-the-streets-of-dublin-for-shane-macgowan-funeral-3556189">因肺炎去世</a>，享年 65 岁，并于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bono-johnny-depp-nick-cave-lead-tributes-to-shane-macgowan-at-funeral-3556257">12 月 8 日下葬</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-line-the-streets-of-dublin-for-shane-macgowan-funeral-3556189">在他的葬礼在爱尔兰蒂珀雷里郡尼纳举行之前，粉丝们聚集在都柏林的街道两旁</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/johnny-depp-salutes-maestro-shane-macgowan-during-funeral-reading-3556302">约翰尼·德普也出席了葬礼</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glen-hansard-and-lisa-oneill-perform-fairytale-of-new-york-at-shane-macgowans-funeral-3556366">格伦·汉萨德</a>和爱尔兰总统迈克尔·D·希金斯。</p><p>为了响应他的去世，多位艺术家向这位歌手表达了音乐敬意，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-darkness-tribute-shane-macgowan-the-pogues-sing-along-dublin-3555749">The Darkness</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-murder-capital-cover-the-pogues-im-a-man-you-dont-meet-every-day-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3553807">The Murder Capital</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-pay-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-with-cover-fairytale-of-new-york-3557369">LCD Soundsystem</a>以及最近的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-cover-the-pogues-fairy-tale-of-new-york-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3562319">The Libertines</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-shane-macgowan-obituary-3562664">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 在新讣告中缅怀肖恩·麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 的帖子：“我是一名粉丝，纯粹而简单，我将永远如此”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Billie Eilish、Dua Lipa、Olivia Rodrigo 入围 2024 年奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲候选名单https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo-oscars-2024-shortlist-best-original-song-3562452?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=billie-eilish- dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo-oscars-2024-入围最佳原创歌曲Eli OrdonezFri, 22 Dec 2023 03:22:02 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3562452 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什、杜阿·利帕和奥利维亚·罗德里戈" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Metro Boomin、Sharon Van Etten、Ludwig Göransson、Jarvis Cocker 等人也在音乐类别中获得提及</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo-oscars-2024-shortlist-best-original-song-3562452">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)、杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 和奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 入围 2024 年奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲入围艺术家名单，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什、杜阿·利帕和奥利维亚·罗德里戈" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>(Billie Eilish)、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo</a> ) 等人都曾入围 2024 年奥斯卡金像奖入围名单。<b></b></p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/barbie-soundtrack-review-film-3471113"><b>《芭比娃娃》原声带评论：品牌歌曲让你心痒痒</b></a></li></ul><p>昨天（12月21日），学院公布了最佳原创歌曲、最佳原创配乐等10个类别的入围名单。 15 首歌曲获得最佳原创歌曲提名，其中包括<i><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie">芭比娃娃</a></i>提交的所有三首歌曲，即 Dua Lipa 的《Dance The Night》、Billie Eilish 的《What Was I Made For?》以及瑞恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-gosling">·高斯林</a>演唱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-ronson">马克·罗森</a>和安德鲁·怀亚特的《我只是肯》。</p><p>其他提及的内容包括奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hunger-games-prequel-confirmed-for-film-adaptation-2651093"><i>《饥饿游戏：鸣鸟与蛇之歌》</i></a>原声带的贡献<i>、</i> 《现在抓不到我》、《我在做梦吗？》由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/a$ap-rocky">A$AP Rocky</a>和 ​​Roisee 主演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/spider-man-across-the-spider-verse-reviews-in-running-best-superhero-film-ever-3451144"><i>《蜘蛛侠：穿越蜘蛛侠宇宙</i></a>》<i>的</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metro-boomin">Metro Boomin</a>策划配乐，席琳·宋 (Celine Song) 突破性首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/past-lives-review-a24-greta-lee-3495175"><i>《前世》</i></a>中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sharon-van-etten">Sharon Van Etten 的</a>《Quiet Eyes》，甚至还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wes-anderson">韦斯·安德森 (Wes Anderson)</a>为他合写的电影贾维斯·科克<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jarvis-cocker">（Jarvis Cocker）</a>以班卓琴为主导的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/asteroid-city-review-wes-andersons-star-stuffed-ufo-adventure-3446917"><i>古怪小行星城</i></a>小曲“亲爱的外星人（天堂中的艺术）”。</p><p>最佳原创配乐入围名单中也有各种各样的名字，从路德维希·戈兰森和约翰·威廉姆斯分别为《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392"><i>奥本海默</i></a>》和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/indiana-jones-dial-of-destiny-review-3446464"><i>夺宝奇兵》和《命运的表盘》</i></a>创作的宽广配乐，到久石让为宫崎骏的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christian-bale-florence-pugh-robert-pattinson-english-dub-cast-studio-ghibli-the-boy-and-the-heron-3516883"><i>《男孩与男孩》</i></a>创作的忧郁配乐。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christian-bale-florence-pugh-robert-pattinson-english-dub-cast-studio-ghibli-the-boy-and-the-heron-3516883"><i>Heron</i></a> 、Daniel Pemberton 为<i>《蜘蛛侠：穿越蜘蛛侠宇宙》</i>制作的电子音景、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-midi">Black Midi</a>合伙人 Jerskin Fendrix 为<i>Poor Things</i>制作的古怪配乐，以及 Mark Ronson 和 Andrew Wyatt 为《<i>芭比娃娃》</i>制作的流行音乐。</p><p>为了回应<em>芭比娃娃的</em>点头，<a href="https://x.com/DUALIPA/status/1737997683363885564?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 在 X 上表达了她的兴奋之情</a>，并发布了她与马克·朗森 (Mark Ronson) 合作的《舞夜》的节选，并写道：“感谢[学院]！！！！多么美好的梦想啊啊啊！！！”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">这个芭比娃娃凭借“Dance The Night”入围 2024 年奥斯卡入围名单<a href="https://twitter.com/MarkRonson?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@MarkRonson</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/carolineailin?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#carolineailin</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/Wyattish?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Wyattish</